column5: I normaly fish the thorah and georgina island areas but would like to try a different area, was thinking the trout/whiskey shoal areas. Would l be thinking in the right direction? TIA

try around strawberry.  You are looking for the same kind of structure as thorah.  Rocks with deeperwater nearby and small clumps of weedbeds randomly placed in sandier locations.  I know that was pretty vague but
HMMMMMM Wondering where my invite was for this adventure,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,just saying,,,
Watch yourself around Strawberry, if you dont know it. BIG ROCKS on the southside.
Hey Brian my son will be with me and I think he is bringing his GF so me tinks your outta luck again. You are welcome to come up to Dalrymple this weekend if you like!
if this bloody wind would just die down a bit I might just make it out there!
